headline: CMS to lower importance of ‘call center’ metric in Medicare Advantage star ratings
summary: Regulators’ assessment of customer support centers has spurred recent lawsuits from UnitedHealthcare, Centene and Humana. But the metric “is going to have a smaller weighting on star ratings moving forward,” the director of Medicare said.
